  hardware/soc_minimal/church_soc.peri.xml
  Pin assignments for the Sapphire SoC minimal UART gate test — Ti60F225.

  db_version="20252999" / version="2025.2.288.4.15": required for 2026.1
  efx_run interface + efx_pnr to read this file without aborting.

  Clock config: GPIOL_P_18 as conn_type="normal" input named "clk" with
  clkmux_buf_name="" and all CLKMUX ROUTE0 name="".  No PLL — 25 MHz crystal
  drives fabric directly.  This is the proven-safe config from soc_combined.

  IO bank voltage assignments (all 12 banks must be declared):
    BL  3.3 V LVCMOS  (UART TX/RX → FT4232H)
    BR  1.8 V LVCMOS  (LED outputs)
    TL  1.8 V LVCMOS  (push button GPIOT_N_06)
    TR  1.8 V LVCMOS
    1A–4B  1.8 V LVCMOS  (unused but declared — required by 2026.1 tools)
-->
